des:
Start your day with a dose of stand up comedy from Andy Kozel. Tune in for a daily dose of his hilariously funny and futile observations. They'll make you laugh, not cry, or just make you feel blah. But, it's a great way to start your day. 
For more humor from Andy Kozel find him on Instagram @Andykozel or on his website at www.andykozel.com
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
